South African celebrity chef Reuben Riffel is doing something new. Reuben s One&amp;Only (at the deluxe One&amp;Only Hotel in Cape Town) presents a business lunch menu that guarantees you ll enjoy a two-course menu in under 60 minutes, or your money back. As one of South Africa s most cherished celebrity chefs, Riffel recently launched new lunch and dinner menus that happily marry sophisticated dining with a moreish brasserie-style menu. The good news is your lunch includes complimentary Wi-Fi and access to the resort s business centre boardroom. For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.